# Unicode.GeneralCategory.enclosingMark

**Case**

An enclosing combining mark.

## Declaration

```swift
case enclosingMark
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Enclosing_Mark` (abbreviated `Me`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
